"Change Set:		7884Files-ar.28Files-ar.28:Adds FileDirectory equality comparison (#hash and #=)."!!FileDirectory methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ar 10/4/2009 22:22'!= aDirectory	"Compare two FileDirectory instances."	^(pathName asString 			compare: aDirectory pathName asString 			caseSensitive: (self isCaseSensitive | aDirectory isCaseSensitive)) = 2! !!FileDirectory methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ar 10/4/2009 21:57'!hash	"Hash is reimplemented because #= is reimplemented"	^pathName asLowercase hash! !